### HTML Semantics
```html
<!-- Use semantic HTML -->
<main>
  <h1>Israel Earthquake Map</h1>
  <section aria-labelledby="map-heading">
    <h2 id="map-heading">Interactive Map</h2>
    <div role="application" aria-label="Earthquake data visualization">
      <!-- Map content -->
    </div>
  </section>
</main>
```

### ARIA Attributes
```html
<!-- Proper ARIA usage -->
<button aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="filter-panel">
  Filters
</button>
<div id="filter-panel" aria-labelledby="filter-button" hidden>
  <!-- Filter content -->
</div>
```

### Focus Management
```css
/* Visible focus indicators */
.button:focus {
  outline: 2px solid var(--color-primary-600);
  outline-offset: 2px;
}

/* Skip links */
.skip-link {
  position: absolute;
  top: -40px;
  left: 6px;
  background: var(--color-primary-600);
  color: white;
  padding: 8px;
  text-decoration: none;
  z-index: 1000;
}

.skip-link:focus {
  top: 6px;
}
```

### Color and Contrast
```css
/* Ensure sufficient contrast */
.text-primary {
  color: var(--text-1); /* 4.5:1 contrast ratio */
}

.text-muted {
  color: var(--text-muted); /* 4.5:1 contrast ratio */
}

/* Don't rely on color alone */
.magnitude-indicator {
  color: var(--mag-moderate);
  font-weight: bold; /* Additional visual indicator */
}
```

